You have to also figure out how you're going to manage direct foreign investment that would go to an open and free Cuba, how you're going to guarantee contracts and that type of a system.

00:28:30.347 --> 00:28:32.800
Florida stands ready to cooperate with a free Cuba.

00:28:32.800 --> 00:28:45.058
We stand ready to do that work.

00:28:45.058 --> 00:29:05.313
Our port systems, both our seaports and our airports, are fully equipped and ready with investment moving through the United States of America coming from Florida to help the Cuban people stabilize that country and then to reopen it as a free society.

00:29:05.313 --> 00:29:09.811
But I want to stress Florida will fully cooperate with a free Cuba.

00:29:09.811 --> 00:29:14.747
Florida will not cooperate with some amalgam of a new dictatorship if the Castros are gone.

00:29:18.736 --> 00:29:19.128
I said they're going to remove all the Castros.

00:29:24.060 --> 00:29:24.280
In the days ahead, I saw Marines, I saw Navy Seals, I saw people coming in the night.

00:29:24.280 --> 00:29:26.160
Now, listen to what he says.

00:29:26.160 --> 00:29:27.160
What did Rubio say?

00:29:27.160 --> 00:29:29.293
Remember when you showed me?

00:29:29.293 --> 00:29:34.027
He said, 'We're not going to tell you where we're going to do it.

00:29:34.027 --> 00:29:40.120
' He said, 'We're not going to tell you when we're going to do this.

00:29:40.120 --> 00:29:43.000
' He goes, 'Why would we tell you?

00:29:43.000 --> 00:29:45.309
' I know it's a dumb question.

00:29:45.309 --> 00:29:46.251
Remember that?

00:29:46.251 --> 00:29:53.131
Well, if you don't want to play that, play the other one with the old man while you're getting that one because it blessed me.

00:29:53.131 --> 00:29:54.608
The gray-headed old guy.

00:29:54.608 --> 00:29:56.780
We got to move quick.

00:30:02.480 --> 00:30:02.680
We're late.

00:30:02.680 --> 00:30:03.800
Play him.

00:30:03.800 --> 00:30:07.664
He left Cuba in 1961 when he was just 15 years old.

00:30:12.304 --> 00:30:12.576
That is correct.

00:30:12.576 --> 00:30:17.853
Tell me about what today means in the news of the indictment of Raúl Castro.

00:30:24.120 --> 00:30:24.325
It means some justice for the Cuban people for 67 years.

00:30:24.325 --> 00:30:29.640
Sorry, we have been ignored by everybody: the United Nations, the Organization of American States, the European Union, everybody.

00:30:41.590 --> 00:30:41.840
So, we hope this is the beginning of the downfall of the Castro regime.

00:30:41.840 --> 00:30:43.700
Sorry, I'm a little emotional.

00:30:53.331 --> 00:30:55.560
And we're ready to go back and help in the reconstruction of our country with work, with money, with investment, and with love that has been lacking in Cuba for the last six decades.

00:30:55.560 --> 00:31:00.413
Oscar, thank you so much for sharing your perspective.

00:31:00.413 --> 00:31:05.600
I know you're getting emotional because this is a huge day for the Cuban community.

00:31:05.600 --> 00:31:08.940
It blessed me because I appreciate it.

00:31:08.940 --> 00:31:10.817
Yeah, met with them recently.

00:31:11.589 --> 00:31:13.480
The CIA director was down there a few weeks ago.

00:31:13.480 --> 00:31:16.495
There's some State Department communications that occur.

00:31:16.495 --> 00:31:21.600
I just don't see a lot of At the end of the day, they got to make a decision.

00:31:23.040 --> 00:31:23.336
Their system doesn't work.

00:31:23.336 --> 00:31:25.297
Their economic system does not work.

00:31:26.644 --> 00:31:26.836
It's broken.

00:31:31.120 --> 00:31:31.440
And you can't fix it with the current political system that's in place.

00:31:31.440 --> 00:31:33.893
They just don't comprehend how to do it.

00:31:41.669 --> 00:31:41.971
And it's a failed state.

00:31:41.971 --> 00:31:54.320
Like their economy and the model they're trying to follow in Cuba doesn't resemble what anyone is doing anywhere in the world.

00:32:01.256 --> 00:32:05.000
I mean, there are other ways to do it that can provide the people of Cuba prosperity and opportunity.

00:32:08.064 --> 00:32:13.720
And it's what I said in the video to them the other day.

00:32:13.720 --> 00:32:20.060
You look at Cuba, the Bahamas, Jamaica, the Dominican Republic, and here in Florida.

00:32:20.060 --> 00:32:37.480
Cuba's surrounded by places where people have the right to do things like own a business, work for themselves, and be able to vote for the leaders that govern them or replace them.

00:32:37.480 --> 00:32:42.904
So, if that's possible all around Cuba, why is that not possible inside of Cuba?

00:32:44.440 --> 00:32:56.472
And right now there just doesn't seem to be people over there in charge of the regime who are in any way open to any of those changes.

00:32:56.472 --> 00:33:00.474
And the things they've talked about economically are cosmetic in nature.

00:33:00.474 --> 00:33:11.728
They're not real because that's what they've gotten used to all these years is just buying time and waiting us out.

00:33:11.728 --> 00:33:16.720
They're not going to be able to wait us out or buy time.

00:33:16.720 --> 00:33:18.853
We're very serious.

00:33:18.853 --> 00:33:20.606
We're very focused.

00:33:20.606 --> 00:33:29.960
As I told you a moment ago in the context of Iran, the president's preference is always a negotiated agreement that's peaceful.

00:33:29.960 --> 00:33:32.320
That's always our preference.

00:33:32.320 --> 00:33:36.600
That remains our preference with Cuba.

00:33:36.600 --> 00:33:38.690
I'm just being honest with you.

00:33:38.690 --> 00:33:47.880
You know, the likelihood of that happening given who we're dealing with right now is not high.

00:33:47.880 --> 00:34:02.480
But if they have a change of heart, we're here, and in the meantime, we'll keep doing what we need to do.

00:34:02.480 --> 00:34:06.400
It sounds a lot like nation building.

00:34:13.720 --> 00:34:14.100
The administration doesn't believe in using force for nation building.

00:34:14.100 --> 00:34:15.966
It's not nation building.

00:34:15.966 --> 00:34:23.824
We are addressing something that's directly related to the national security of the United States.

00:34:23.824 --> 00:34:26.935
We are involved in places all over the world.

00:34:26.935 --> 00:34:31.080
You're asking me about Ebola.

00:34:31.080 --> 00:34:36.133
Important, but Ebola is in Africa.

00:34:36.133 --> 00:34:39.782
Cuba's 90 miles from our shores.

00:34:39.782 --> 00:35:01.520
So if you have a systemic meltdown in that country, which is where they're headed, their power plants, by the way, the reason why their power plants break down, they've been having blackouts for years.

00:35:01.520 --> 00:35:08.903
They had major blackouts last year, and they were still getting free Venezuelan oil.

00:35:25.310 --> 00:35:25.500
They haven't spent a penny in fixing their energy production or their electrical grid.

00:35:30.240 --> 00:35:33.520
They don't spend any money on that stuff; they pocket it.

00:35:33.960 --> 00:35:46.400
They have a private military company named GAESA who's sitting on $18 billion of assets, and not a penny of that transfers over to the state budget.

00:35:46.400 --> 00:35:53.049
Not a penny of that goes over to help the people of Cuba—not one cent.

00:35:53.049 --> 00:36:16.556
So even if they had all the diesel in the world, they still wouldn't be able to generate energy because they've stolen the money and haven't invested in their energy infrastructure.

00:36:16.556 --> 00:36:19.730
So you're heading for a failed state.

00:36:19.730 --> 00:36:22.040
That's what you have now.

00:36:41.111 --> 00:36:48.512
But it's 90 miles from our shores, so we'll be impacted by the migratory crisis, by any violence and instability that happens there.

00:37:10.825 --> 00:37:11.260
It directly implicates the United States' national interest.

00:37:14.820 --> 00:37:21.607
So the future of Cuba belongs to the people of Cuba in terms of how they're governed, what the system looks like, and so forth.

00:37:21.960 --> 00:37:33.110
But the national security threat is 100% something we're going to focus on because that's about America.

00:37:33.390 --> 00:37:34.200
I loved it.

00:37:34.200 --> 00:37:35.280
Praise the Lord.

00:37:35.280 --> 00:37:40.049
It's time for the Cuban people to have a major revival.

00:37:40.049 --> 00:37:53.187
And as I saw in this, I saw that leader sacrificing chickens and drinking the blood down in what looked like a cellar below this house.

00:38:10.790 --> 00:38:11.185
It was a beautiful white house with a red roof that had tiles on it.

00:38:11.185 --> 00:38:16.693
And he was killing these chickens and looking at President Trump's picture.

00:38:23.280 --> 00:38:41.246
And as he was doing this—and I don't focus on the darkness—I saw him start to shapeshift into a dog, his face, but I saw a man in the corner who had antlers on his head, doing some kind of dance with his shirt off, and they were doing satanic stuff against our president.

00:38:48.920 --> 00:38:49.126
And the Lord said, 'Intercede.

00:38:49.126 --> 00:39:08.840
' And I saw they had a lead case with a device that could not be sniffed out by our sniffers that was given to them by the Russian government from the 1960s Cuban Missile Crisis.

00:39:11.074 --> 00:39:13.680
They have weapons that we don't know they have.

00:39:13.680 --> 00:39:28.200
But as I saw this, he was going to set this thing off trying to retaliate from America coming within to make it uninhabitable on this mountain.

00:39:28.200 --> 00:39:51.460
There was a mountain there, and they had a base in this mountain, and there were gold coins and gold bars all inside of this mountain and $100 bills, and they put it on a boat.

00:39:51.460 --> 00:39:53.406
He didn't fly out.

00:39:53.406 --> 00:40:00.720
He went to the Dominican Republic through a system in Cuba to get away.

00:40:04.166 --> 00:40:08.554
And he got in a boat and Claudia kept him—Claudia kept him in Mexico at a resort, hiding the leader of Cuba.

00:40:08.554 --> 00:40:17.510
In the days ahead, he goes to the Dominican Republic and flies out in a private jet.

00:40:17.510 --> 00:40:20.400
He didn't fly out of Cuba.

00:40:20.400 --> 00:40:32.703
He took a boat, and it's 400 miles away to the Dominican Republic from what I understand from the point of Cuba where I saw him leaving.

00:40:32.703 --> 00:40:36.080
So, this is the kind of stuff I saw.

00:40:39.880 --> 00:40:50.640
And I saw when it comes to the CIA, I saw projects that were dark, that were worse than waterboarding in these rooms.

00:40:59.752 --> 00:41:00.064
I saw things that were very dark.

00:41:01.624 --> 00:41:06.400
But the Lord said he was exposing things, and I saw finances coming to Cuba from America with investments.

00:41:21.840 --> 00:41:22.005
But the Lord said, 'Pay attention to Cuba.

00:41:30.240 --> 00:41:30.400
Don't underestimate your enemy.

00:41:30.400 --> 00:41:32.480
' How many times the Lord said that?

00:41:32.480 --> 00:41:33.620
'Don't underestimate your enemy.

00:41:33.620 --> 00:41:34.250
Watch Cuba.

00:41:34.250 --> 00:41:34.880
Watch Cuba.

00:41:34.880 --> 00:41:38.520
' And I've had video after video; the Lord said, 'Watch Cuba.

00:41:38.520 --> 00:41:40.293
' The mules, the balseros.

00:41:40.293 --> 00:41:41.587
Don't underestimate your enemy.

00:41:41.587 --> 00:41:52.920
The Lord said they're cocky; 'We're going to do this, we're going to do that.

00:41:52.920 --> 00:42:12.571
' But I say they have a stronghold of people with blue uniforms that are the resistance to this because they're loyal to the Castros and to the leader there now.

00:42:14.297 --> 00:42:17.794
And I saw a loyalty that I was praying, 'Lay down your arms.

00:42:17.794 --> 00:42:38.693
' But I saw gang leaders like MS-13 gang leaders—that's the only way to tell, I don't know how else to say it—in Cuba that were like drug lords for prostitution, drug trafficking, and such coming out of Cuba that was connected to Colombia and Venezuela.

00:42:49.870 --> 00:42:50.015
They were like bosses, but I saw a free Cuba coming.

00:42:51.560 --> 00:43:11.023
But there were our men and women of service that we pray over who would go in in the middle of the night and invade with tech like I've never seen.

00:43:29.640 --> 00:43:29.895
I saw it go dark with cyber warfare to be able to infiltrate and take over more easily.

00:43:35.000 --> 00:43:36.120
But he was in a bunker in the mountain.

00:43:36.120 --> 00:43:46.900
He was in a bunker, and there was one way in and there was a secret way out, and I saw they couldn't get out with a helicopter.

00:43:46.900 --> 00:44:04.240
So, those are the things we've been praying over for quite a while and now we see this stuff in the news today.

00:44:04.240 --> 00:44:14.520
It hasn't happened yet, but we see the birthing pains of it.

00:44:17.263 --> 00:44:17.480
So, it's pretty accurate so far.

00:44:19.309 --> 00:44:20.653
To the people who don't believe in it, you don't have to watch.

00:44:20.653 --> 00:44:26.125
But I'm telling you, a great revival, I believe, is coming to Cuba and a great shaking to awaken.

00:44:26.125 --> 00:44:31.580
And I believe with all my heart, it's sooner than later.

00:44:31.580 --> 00:44:33.085
Why?

00:44:33.085 --> 00:44:39.266
Because we're looking at the end of the end.

00:45:04.151 --> 00:45:04.409
And God said, 'I want the Cuban people to have a major revival.

00:45:04.409 --> 00:45:08.171
' So when the day happens, you'll remember the Lord said it.

00:45:08.171 --> 00:45:11.312
The Lord said it, not Brandon.

00:45:11.312 --> 00:45:18.629
We always attract to deflect; it's always about giving glory to Jesus.

00:45:42.780 --> 00:45:43.050
The same with Israel striking Iran.

00:45:43.320 --> 00:45:54.176
I said in the days ahead, I did not see America striking Iran anymore.

00:46:16.460 --> 00:46:16.650
I saw Israel doing it and people get very mad at Israel for what they're about to do.

00:46:16.650 --> 00:46:17.410
America pulls back.

00:46:30.560 --> 00:46:30.840
I saw America pulling back and Israel going full force one time.

00:46:30.840 --> 00:46:31.400
Boom.

00:46:31.400 --> 00:46:34.295
With devices we've never seen used before.

00:46:34.295 --> 00:46:37.095
And it would be used on the mountain.

00:46:37.095 --> 00:46:41.520
And the mountain was glowing in the dark.

00:46:43.040 --> 00:46:44.560
It was glowing.

00:46:44.560 --> 00:47:03.670
Now, I know that's a metaphor—I don't think it really is glowing with green light—but I saw Israel about to use tech with some kind of device that has never been used before.

00:47:05.458 --> 00:47:12.170
And it made the mountain where you couldn't go in it to get this uranium.

00:47:12.170 --> 00:47:12.700
Okay?

00:47:19.160 --> 00:47:19.486
And I said, 'Watch, pray for Israel.

00:47:19.486 --> 00:47:25.587
' I saw an attack coming against Israel that was worse than the one that happened in October.

00:47:26.600 --> 00:47:28.512
It happens in the middle of the night.

00:47:28.512 --> 00:47:31.888
They use chemical weapons on the people this time with sprayers.

00:47:46.640 --> 00:47:47.240
It was a mustard-looking color.

00:47:48.387 --> 00:47:49.480
It was yellow.

00:47:50.662 --> 00:48:05.660
And they spray them and the trucks come out of the mountain and they're brought across Syria into Damascus, coming across Iraq at the top, and they brought it in a truck and they were 50-gallon drums and they gave it to, I believe it was like Hezbollah.

00:48:05.660 --> 00:48:19.560
So, those are the things we're praying over because I saw them trying to strike Israel, and so we continue to pray for Israel.

00:48:19.560 --> 00:48:23.020
We believe we have power and authority and we pray for the peace of Jerusalem.

00:48:23.020 --> 00:48:25.160
We pray for the peace of Israel.

00:48:35.635 --> 00:48:35.820
We pray for the covering over their people, their innocent people, and we pray that Iran is liberated.

00:48:36.375 --> 00:48:54.220
The Lord said, 'I'm bringing a great revival to Iran and I will shake Iran for the underground church will rise up and they will have a window.

00:48:54.220 --> 00:49:04.390
' And the Lord said, 'Pray for the gray-headed man with the bald head, the prince, because they said in the days ahead, I saw him be assassinated.

00:49:04.390 --> 00:49:19.912
' And the Lord said, 'Pray for Reza Pahlavi.

00:49:19.912 --> 00:49:29.858
' I saw him being a leader there for a season, trying to speak out and do stuff, but then they took him out with a sniper.

00:49:29.858 --> 00:49:35.000
He was speaking and I saw a new leader coming up out of Iran.

00:49:50.440 --> 00:49:50.709
But when this happened, the Prince of Persia shrunk back for a season and I saw Iraq coming up and I saw blessing coming up out of Iraq.

00:49:50.709 --> 00:50:00.730
I know I go over these words a lot, but there's a lot of things the Lord gives us and it gets buried and people accuse you.

00:50:00.730 --> 00:50:02.055
'Well, Brandon is buried.

00:50:02.055 --> 00:50:05.755
We don't know what you say all the time.

00:50:25.600 --> 00:50:26.027
You speak for three hours.

00:50:26.027 --> 00:50:30.725
' I don't want anybody to get lost in this.

00:50:47.600 --> 00:50:48.360
And I am not trying to hide anything.

00:50:49.880 --> 00:50:59.210
I try to bring everything out as much as I can remember to rehash it so you'll remember it, because I believe in my heart it will come to pass.

00:51:15.005 --> 00:51:15.310
So, here we are.

00:51:15.310 --> 00:51:17.491
Let's see what happens next.

00:51:17.491 --> 00:51:24.760
Praying over Taiwan for an invasion from China, with North Korea being a part of it.

00:51:24.760 --> 00:51:25.993
Praying over Ukraine and Russia.

00:51:25.993 --> 00:51:35.200
I'm curious about what happened with the meeting with him and Xi, and the big event they had this week.

00:51:35.200 --> 00:51:40.227
They had a cooking class together; I thought that was kind of fun.

00:51:40.227 --> 00:51:43.480
They did a cooking thing.

00:51:43.480 --> 00:51:47.745
Best friends that could hold hands.

00:52:03.968 --> 00:52:04.120
I thought, "Are they having a cooking party?

00:52:04.120 --> 00:52:05.867
They're making dumplings and stuff.

00:52:05.867 --> 00:52:08.575
" Isn't that kind of interesting?

00:52:08.575 --> 00:52:12.446
Two men like that having a dumpling party, making some kind of crepes.

00:52:24.820 --> 00:52:25.070
I thought it was kind of funny.

00:52:25.070 --> 00:52:27.580
I guess it shows they like cooking, but whatever.

00:52:27.580 --> 00:52:32.887
Next, look, see, they even have a portrait together.

00:52:32.887 --> 00:52:39.900
They're all hanging together in a portrait.

00:52:39.900 --> 00:52:41.556
It's a painting.

00:52:41.556 --> 00:52:42.644
They're like best friends.

00:52:42.644 --> 00:52:46.415
I'm surprised they're not holding hands.

00:52:46.415 --> 00:52:48.387
Putin's excited about it.

00:52:48.387 --> 00:52:49.320
Best friends, I guess.

00:52:51.640 --> 00:52:52.620
Is Trump not invited?

00:52:52.620 --> 00:53:00.794
He didn't get to be in the picture.

00:53:00.794 --> 00:53:09.580
I wonder what Trump's thinking: "Well, you didn't make a picture of me.

00:53:09.580 --> 00:53:12.577
" Look, they could put their flags together.

00:53:12.577 --> 00:53:13.400
Let's clap.

00:53:13.400 --> 00:53:14.589
2026, 2027—what's happening?

00:53:14.589 --> 00:53:15.869
Oh, shake hands.

00:53:15.869 --> 00:53:17.423
"You're my friend.

00:53:17.423 --> 00:53:19.800
See, we did more than Trump and you, right?

00:53:39.265 --> 00:53:39.550
" A hundred thousand Russians study Chinese, including 20,000 in educational courses in China, right?

00:53:39.550 --> 00:53:41.880
Their kids are starting to learn Russian.

00:53:44.840 --> 00:53:45.012
So, they let him start Russian.

00:53:45.012 --> 00:53:46.216
They're going to shake hands.

00:53:56.500 --> 00:53:56.710
And then they did oil deals.

00:53:58.436 --> 00:54:00.060
I swear, didn't you hear President Trump say my party was better than his?

00:54:03.646 --> 00:54:03.874
What we do was better than theirs.

00:54:04.331 --> 00:54:06.000
I thought it was funny; I laughed.

00:54:06.000 --> 00:54:06.780
They're so competitive.

00:54:06.780 --> 00:54:11.736
Look, there they are again, shaking hands.

00:54:11.736 --> 00:54:13.370
Unity being shown.

00:54:13.370 --> 00:54:14.920
Now, this is interesting.

00:54:14.920 --> 00:54:18.960
These men were on a hidden assignment to attack Israel.

00:54:18.960 --> 00:54:23.260
Look how they are hiding.

00:54:23.260 --> 00:54:46.020
They were going into Israel to attack.

00:54:46.020 --> 00:54:47.253
You see them?

00:54:47.253 --> 00:54:54.095
They're hiding in a trailer bed on a semi, similar to the way I saw the children being smuggled in from Mexico.

00:54:59.189 --> 00:54:59.463
This is a semi-trailer bed and they're hiding in there.

00:55:09.830 --> 00:55:10.100
That's the driver.

00:55:10.100 --> 00:55:14.448
They don't show the whole semi; this is just the bed of it.

00:55:14.448 --> 00:55:16.880
But at least they caught them.

00:55:16.880 --> 00:55:19.885
They didn't have anything in the load.

00:55:35.680 --> 00:55:36.703
It would probably have been more believable going down the highway with some bananas or something in it.

00:55:36.703 --> 00:55:38.949
Pretty dumb.

00:55:38.949 --> 00:55:42.480
Next, he indicted that Castro, and then NASA.

00:55:42.480 --> 00:55:52.053
Remember I said in the days ahead—remember this before they even said it—I put it in the picture at the beginning of the year.

00:55:52.053 --> 00:55:57.190
NASA says they're going to build the new moon base.

00:55:57.190 --> 00:56:06.200
Tuesday, May 26, is a live news event where we'll share updates on our lunar exploration plans.

00:56:06.200 --> 00:56:14.489
They want to build a new moon base, and this is what we're hearing today.

00:56:14.489 --> 00:56:16.030
Go back to the picture.

00:56:22.448 --> 00:56:22.944
I told you this was coming at the beginning of the year.

00:56:26.680 --> 00:56:29.484
I said they're going to talk about making a moon base and it will be in the news a lot.

00:56:29.484 --> 00:56:30.160
Here it is.

