We told you about it clear back here.

00:56:58.520 --> 00:56:59.853
Where's the moon base?

00:56:59.853 --> 00:57:00.920
That's the rocket.

00:57:00.920 --> 00:57:06.880
See, I told Braden to make it next to the rocket.

00:57:12.000 --> 00:57:12.273
And they did it.

00:57:12.273 --> 00:57:20.491
They put the men in it just like the Lord said, and it went around the moon.

00:57:33.062 --> 00:57:33.293
I said they're going to make a moon base right next to it.

00:57:33.293 --> 00:57:34.449
Do you see that?

00:57:34.449 --> 00:57:37.284
This is what we gave you for January.

00:57:37.284 --> 00:57:42.000
These are all the things we saw back in September, October, and November.

00:57:42.000 --> 00:57:44.640
Then I said they were going to invade Iran again.

00:57:44.640 --> 00:57:47.580
Look, that was what the bomber was.

00:57:49.035 --> 00:57:50.668
And they did it.

00:57:50.668 --> 00:57:55.270
Look at the oil wells burning.

00:58:13.560 --> 00:58:13.815
I said the oil wells will burn.

00:58:13.815 --> 00:58:15.603
It's all glory to God.

00:58:22.131 --> 00:58:22.509
People ask me all the time, "Brandon, have you missed it before?

00:58:22.509 --> 00:58:25.880
" Yes, I have.

00:58:25.880 --> 00:58:30.080
I've missed it, and I'm learning just like everybody else.

00:58:30.080 --> 00:58:36.657
You go through life and you learn through trial and error.

00:58:36.657 --> 00:58:43.257
Some lessons are harder than others, but that's how you learn.

00:58:43.257 --> 00:58:49.142
When you stumble and fall, you pick yourself up and keep walking.

00:58:49.142 --> 00:58:51.756
Do you remember the blood moons back in 2015?

00:58:51.756 --> 00:58:56.790
That was a time of learning.

00:58:56.800 --> 00:59:00.533
Look at this.

00:59:00.533 --> 00:59:01.813
May 27.

00:59:19.200 --> 00:59:19.587
This is the new Passion of the Christ.

00:59:32.027 --> 00:59:32.593
The Lord said he was going to use this film to bring in a great harvest.

00:59:32.593 --> 00:59:33.770
That's exciting.

00:59:34.990 --> 00:59:36.500
This is what we've been praying for.

00:59:36.500 --> 00:59:37.400
Mel Gibson.

00:59:37.400 --> 00:59:38.631
Is that the Jesus?

00:59:49.480 --> 00:59:49.738
I think so.

01:00:02.840 --> 01:00:03.230
It looks kind of like Jim Caviezel, doesn't he?

01:00:08.071 --> 01:00:08.427
I hope he's a good Jesus.

01:00:08.427 --> 01:00:10.204
We saw great revivals.

01:00:10.204 --> 01:00:18.900
We were praying for the theaters and for Mel Gibson to keep accurate with the Word.

01:00:18.900 --> 01:00:25.100
We saw a great revival coming forth out of theaters.

01:00:25.100 --> 01:00:37.688
I saw people stationed in theaters who went to all of them with tracts to witness to the people as they were crying.

01:00:37.688 --> 01:00:42.200
They were able to be reached.

01:00:51.927 --> 01:00:54.218
I saw people who spent their whole day there handing out tracts to the ones who needed Jesus.

01:00:54.218 --> 01:01:01.020
Some of the theaters didn't say anything because they bought a ticket and just went out.

01:01:01.020 --> 01:01:07.080
The church stationed people at these theaters to bring in the harvest.

01:01:07.080 --> 01:01:14.680
I believe it will be a huge box office hit.

01:01:14.680 --> 01:01:22.720
Moving on, I was praying for this pastor in California.

01:01:22.720 --> 01:01:33.920
The Lord showed us a man that God was going to use on the West Coast to be a place of revival like Azusa Street.

01:01:33.920 --> 01:01:40.447
The Lord said He's going to do something very different at this man's church.

01:01:40.447 --> 01:01:43.910
He has a gray beard.

01:01:43.910 --> 01:01:52.160
Braden found him because of the comments saying, "This is who he is.

01:01:52.160 --> 01:01:53.933
" His name is Joe Sweet.

01:01:53.933 --> 01:02:06.107
I'm sorry if I butcher your name, sir, but the Lord was showing us about this pastor in California and that he will have Shekinah worship.

01:02:06.107 --> 01:02:09.160
That's what we saw also.

01:02:09.160 --> 01:02:13.480
Then concerning John Kilpatrick and finances, those were the highlights.

01:02:13.480 --> 01:02:19.800
I know I probably already went an hour of it, so we'll just stop now.

01:02:19.800 --> 01:02:22.504
It's pretty close to an hour.

01:02:22.504 --> 01:02:34.569
I saw a major revival coming to this church; it would come out of prayer and it would shake the area.

01:02:34.569 --> 01:02:35.783
It would shake California.

01:02:46.000 --> 01:02:46.473
And the Lord said, "You've asked me, Brandon, about the West Coast...

01:02:46.473 --> 01:02:52.300
" You've asked me about pastors on the West Coast.

01:02:58.624 --> 01:02:58.852
And he said, "I'm going to use this man.

01:02:58.852 --> 01:03:00.805
" I'm not familiar with his ministry.

01:03:00.805 --> 01:03:07.067
I don't even know if he preaches the Word of Faith or whatever he preaches.

01:03:30.491 --> 01:03:30.997
I believe if the Lord tells me about him, obviously he's going to be a man of integrity and he's going to walk with the glory because that's what it takes.

01:03:33.019 --> 01:03:34.707
I just tell you what I see.

01:03:34.707 --> 01:03:40.116
You say, "Well, I don't like him.

01:03:40.116 --> 01:03:42.693
" I don't care what you like.

01:03:42.693 --> 01:03:48.140
I'm telling you what the Lord said.

01:03:48.140 --> 01:03:48.720
Whatever.

01:03:48.720 --> 01:03:56.627
I know that the Lord's going to use this man.

01:03:56.627 --> 01:04:08.427
That's what the Lord told me and that's what I stand by when I hear something like that.

01:04:08.427 --> 01:04:13.560
But I was not seeing Bethel.

01:04:13.560 --> 01:04:21.630
People say, "What about Bethel?

01:04:21.640 --> 01:04:22.665
" I haven't seen Bethel.

01:04:22.665 --> 01:04:26.480
I've seen some things about Bethel, but I keep that to myself.

01:04:42.875 --> 01:04:43.220
I just pray over them.

01:04:43.220 --> 01:04:46.349
I'm not here to be a spiritual police.

01:04:46.349 --> 01:04:53.880
I'm here to tell you what the Lord tells me to say, and I walk away from it.

01:04:53.880 --> 01:04:56.023
All right, let's take communion and pray.

01:04:56.023 --> 01:05:00.400
I'm not picking any congregation.

01:05:05.015 --> 01:05:09.223
I have to be careful because I don't want to grieve the Holy Spirit or I'll get in trouble.

01:05:19.926 --> 01:05:20.211
I'm not picking on anybody.

01:05:35.580 --> 01:05:35.800
The Lord just said specifically: "This man with the gray beard.

01:05:35.800 --> 01:05:45.580
" Know that I'm not picking on churches because I'd have to repent and come back here and tell you I got corrected.

01:05:45.580 --> 01:05:48.160
That's not my job.

01:06:03.700 --> 01:06:03.920
The Lord didn't tell me to do that.

01:06:03.920 --> 01:06:14.726
If he tells me, I'm always bold about it, but I do it in a way that is not rude.

01:06:14.994 --> 01:06:28.240
You can correct without having to be rude like that.

01:06:35.460 --> 01:06:35.795
I watch certain people and I see—it doesn't matter.

01:06:35.795 --> 01:06:39.630
Father, I thank you for the body.

01:06:45.280 --> 01:06:50.427
I thank you that we're always in the right place at the right time doing what you've asked us to do.

01:06:56.258 --> 01:06:56.480
I'm so grateful, Father, that you've called us to the kingdom for such a time as this.

01:06:56.480 --> 01:07:00.806
We're healed and whole and well in the name of Jesus.

01:07:00.806 --> 01:07:05.415
There's an expiration date to everything we've been believing for.

01:07:05.415 --> 01:07:08.440
It's time to believe God for bigger.

01:07:21.880 --> 01:07:25.560
Lord, I didn't obey you, did I?

01:07:25.560 --> 01:07:26.680
I saw this.

01:07:26.680 --> 01:07:28.120
Give me a couple more minutes.

01:07:28.120 --> 01:07:33.809
Let's take communion and I'm going to tell you what I saw.

01:07:48.310 --> 01:07:48.640
He told me to tell you about this angel.

01:07:56.368 --> 01:08:02.653
I take this body in the name of Jesus, and we lift it up before you.

01:08:02.653 --> 01:08:09.320
We thank you, Lord, that we are healed and whole and well in the name of Jesus.

01:08:09.320 --> 01:08:15.595
We give you glory, honor, and praise in the mighty name of Jesus.

01:08:15.595 --> 01:08:23.720
By your stripes, Lord, we are healed, and we take this body right now in Jesus' name.

01:08:23.720 --> 01:08:26.404
Now we take the blood.

01:08:26.404 --> 01:08:30.680
We make much of the blood, and the blood makes much of us.

01:08:30.680 --> 01:08:40.239
Forgive us of our sins and any open doors, whatever it may be, Lord.

01:08:40.239 --> 01:08:46.644
We cover it in the blood, and we thank you, Lord, that it never loses its power.

01:08:46.644 --> 01:08:54.886
Great is your faithfulness to us, Lord, as we yield to you, Holy Spirit.

01:08:54.886 --> 01:09:01.924
We thank you that we are uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

01:09:01.924 --> 01:09:06.480
We apply the blood of Jesus over this atmosphere.

01:09:06.480 --> 01:09:14.560
We thank you, Lord, for the angels of the Lord camped around and about us.

01:09:14.560 --> 01:09:17.333
We apply the blood in Jesus' name.

01:09:17.333 --> 01:09:19.030
We fear God and not man.

01:09:19.030 --> 01:09:21.240
Amen and amen.

01:09:32.535 --> 01:09:32.751
I thank you, Lord.

01:09:34.264 --> 01:09:35.382
I hear your voice, and a stranger's voice I will not follow.

01:09:35.382 --> 01:09:36.874
We will not follow.

01:09:36.874 --> 01:09:41.988
I apply the blood of Jesus and thank you, Lord, for the blood.

01:09:41.988 --> 01:09:46.893
It covers me from the top of my head to the soles of my feet.

01:09:54.886 --> 01:09:55.143
The blood of Jesus covers me in Jesus' name.

01:09:55.143 --> 01:09:55.850
Amen and amen.

01:09:55.850 --> 01:09:56.600
Do you believe that?

01:09:56.600 --> 01:10:03.200
If he wants to show us anything, we'll see it uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

01:10:03.200 --> 01:10:04.107
Praise the Lord.

01:10:04.107 --> 01:10:07.400
I'm going to get to this real quick.

01:10:11.080 --> 01:10:12.455
The Lord said the black onyx is connected to the angel.

01:10:12.455 --> 01:10:20.320
Do you remember I told you I was in a group with the man with no face?

01:10:20.320 --> 01:10:29.712
An angel walked up to me and I wanted to tell people about this investment, but the angel put his hands on my lips.

01:10:38.280 --> 01:10:38.840
He had the most beautiful blue eyes and he said, "They're not dead; they can't hear it.

01:10:38.840 --> 01:10:41.000
They're not dead.

01:10:41.000 --> 01:10:43.067
They can't hear it.

01:10:43.067 --> 01:10:47.740
" Until they're dead to self, they won't have ears to hear what the Spirit is saying.

01:10:49.380 --> 01:10:49.730
I said, "I want to tell the people.

01:10:51.052 --> 01:10:52.348
I want to tell them so bad.

01:10:52.348 --> 01:10:54.220
They need to know what's coming.

01:11:08.560 --> 01:11:08.720
" I was outside and it was cold.

01:11:11.211 --> 01:11:13.440
I could see the mulberry bush, and there were red mulberries all over the bush.

01:11:28.320 --> 01:11:28.600
The angel said, "Pay attention to when the berries turn the deepest red.

01:11:28.600 --> 01:11:35.230
This is a sign for you.

01:11:49.040 --> 01:11:58.165
" I went over to an Aston Martin—which I don't have, but I went over to this car and I believe it's symbolic for something—and I breathed on the glass and I wrote the name of this company.

01:11:59.354 --> 01:12:06.000
I was going to do it with my finger, but I'm not going to do it.

01:12:19.591 --> 01:12:20.015
The angel said, "Hush now.

01:12:20.015 --> 01:12:21.710
They're not dead.

01:12:21.720 --> 01:12:25.253
They can't see it.

01:12:25.947 --> 01:12:27.584
" I said, "But I want—" I was transparent.

01:12:27.584 --> 01:12:28.764
They couldn't see me.

01:12:38.600 --> 01:12:38.800
I was dead.

01:12:39.200 --> 01:12:40.900
I thought, "Man, they can't see me.

01:12:55.269 --> 01:12:55.606
I'm yelling as loud as I can and I'm even trying to write it on the glass," and they said they can't see it.

01:12:55.606 --> 01:13:01.936
Then I went inside and I was having a big Christmas party.

01:13:01.936 --> 01:13:04.256
My wife was in a white kitchen.

01:13:04.256 --> 01:13:07.520
She was getting the refreshments and things for everybody.

01:13:09.008 --> 01:13:12.434
The kitchen was a beautiful white, glowing with purity.

01:13:12.434 --> 01:13:14.964
There were white countertops, white shelves, white everything.

01:13:24.600 --> 01:13:24.800
The white lights were so bright when she came out, it was blinding.

01:13:24.800 --> 01:13:29.657
There was a massive TV that was playing the news and the stocks.

01:13:29.657 --> 01:13:36.053
Outside the window, I could see snow falling and I could see the blue car down below.

01:13:36.320 --> 01:13:40.978
I saw all these people so excited about certain investments that had happened and matured.

01:13:40.978 --> 01:13:45.200
They were dressed in big Cosby sweaters.

01:13:45.200 --> 01:13:48.920
You know those big, nice 80s Cosby sweaters?

01:13:48.920 --> 01:13:52.920
They had beautiful sweaters on with all kinds of colors.

01:13:52.920 --> 01:13:55.600
They were puffy and beautiful.

01:14:09.784 --> 01:14:10.112
They were celebrating and so excited.

01:14:25.720 --> 01:14:26.000
I was yelling, "You don't know what's coming!

01:14:34.629 --> 01:14:34.937
There's a storm coming!

01:14:41.520 --> 01:14:41.800
You don't know what's coming!

01:14:41.800 --> 01:14:44.480
" But they couldn't hear me.

01:14:44.480 --> 01:14:49.133
I ran over to a pot that was in front of me.

01:14:49.133 --> 01:14:58.010
The pot was tempered; it had dings all over it and was distressed.

01:15:19.227 --> 01:15:19.653
I breathed on the pot and I wrote into the pot.

01:15:19.653 --> 01:15:27.001
My wife came out and she said, "I see it!

01:15:45.756 --> 01:15:45.951
I see it!

01:15:45.951 --> 01:15:46.733
I see it!

01:15:46.733 --> 01:15:49.951
" But by the time she said she saw it, everybody else saw it.

01:15:49.951 --> 01:15:51.880
But it was too late.

01:16:06.320 --> 01:16:06.630
They were looking at the screen, and the stock market crashed.

01:16:06.630 --> 01:16:10.514
One of the largest crashes in American history happens.

01:16:21.680 --> 01:16:22.085
It goes to the 1930s in just a matter of seconds.

01:16:22.085 --> 01:16:29.298
They were standing on a rug, and the rug was pulled out from underneath them.

01:16:29.298 --> 01:16:33.580
They were so excited for what they had, but they didn't know what was coming.

01:16:33.580 --> 01:16:35.646
There was something so much more.

01:16:35.646 --> 01:16:58.400
As I was driving today, the Lord said, "There are certain things that you can only say in code, because those that have ears to hear will hear, and it will confirm to them what they're supposed to hear.

01:17:12.105 --> 01:17:12.410
But the rest of them cannot handle it.

01:17:12.410 --> 01:17:17.909
You'll be held accountable for the ones that can't handle it if it destroys their lives.

01:17:17.909 --> 01:17:20.815
" That's what he said to me today.

01:17:20.815 --> 01:17:26.480
He said, "You'll be held accountable in the spirit realm for it.

01:17:26.480 --> 01:17:29.609
What is it to gain the whole world and lose your soul?

01:17:29.609 --> 01:17:31.600
" That's what he said.

01:17:31.600 --> 01:17:40.630
So, I've meditated on what things I can say and what I can't, based on what I believe the Lord has said to me.

01:17:40.630 --> 01:17:44.211
What is it to gain the whole world and lose your soul?

01:17:44.211 --> 01:17:52.295
Some people can't handle it.

01:17:52.295 --> 01:17:57.783
They'll never be able to handle it because they aren't "dead" yet.

01:17:57.783 --> 01:18:02.760
Where they're dead, it will not destroy them because they're already dead.

01:18:08.431 --> 01:18:08.889
A dead man tells no tales.

01:18:11.644 --> 01:18:12.568
A dead man—like it was—that's Johnny Depp, right?

01:18:12.876 --> 01:18:16.013
A dead man doesn't have emotions.

01:18:16.013 --> 01:18:17.865
He's dead.

01:18:31.200 --> 01:18:31.455
It's like Billy Burke told me.

01:18:42.667 --> 01:18:43.013
He said, 'Brandon, you could scream at a coffin and none of them are ever moved by it because as dead as they are, they don't care because they're not there.

01:18:43.013 --> 01:18:44.440
' And Kathryn Kuhlman was dead.

01:18:44.440 --> 01:18:47.989
People were talking so much smack about her.

01:18:47.989 --> 01:18:55.391
He said, 'I was in a mall and there were these bullies and they were just ridiculing her.

01:18:55.391 --> 01:19:01.120
' Billy wanted to fight because he was so upset because these guys were saying stuff.

01:19:01.120 --> 01:19:03.583
He said, 'Ms.

01:19:03.583 --> 01:19:08.447
Kuhlman, do you not hear what they're saying?

01:19:08.447 --> 01:19:18.942
' She said, 'Oh, Billy, there are so many things that I learned from the elders like that.

01:19:21.874 --> 01:19:33.797
No matter what somebody says about you, no matter what they're going to say, if they hate you now, they're really going to hate you in the future.

01:19:51.280 --> 01:20:01.167
The Lord already said they are going to hate you for what I'm about to do with you.

01:20:01.167 --> 01:20:03.166
They're going to hate you.

01:20:03.166 --> 01:20:08.685
I'll make you worth billions and they're going to hate you.

01:20:23.876 --> 01:20:24.031
Are you willing to take it?

01:20:24.031 --> 01:20:29.857
I'm going to make you a billionaire through some of the things that I teach you.

01:20:29.857 --> 01:20:32.191
' And folks, he's already made me blessed.

01:20:32.964 --> 01:20:38.770
I invest and do exactly what he's asked me to do.

01:20:44.290 --> 01:20:44.780
I took $10,000 and made it into a bunch because I listen to him.

01:21:05.400 --> 01:21:05.738
So don't hate me whenever you see that I'm blessed, because I've taken the time to listen to him.

01:21:05.738 --> 01:21:09.944
I ask nothing from any of you.

01:21:09.944 --> 01:21:14.720
Never have I ever asked for a dime.

01:21:14.720 --> 01:21:18.165
Never have I solicited you for money.

01:21:18.165 --> 01:21:18.595
Ever.

01:21:18.595 --> 01:21:23.820
But know when these investments mature, know they're coming.

01:21:23.820 --> 01:21:28.629
Know this: the Rolls-Royce that I buy, you didn't pay for.

01:21:30.653 --> 01:21:31.560
The Rolexes that I buy, you never paid for.

01:21:31.560 --> 01:21:36.071
So when it takes place, don't hate me for it because you didn't buy it.

01:21:37.840 --> 01:21:41.200
I listen to the voice of the Lord and I do what he asks me to do.

01:21:56.160 --> 01:21:56.567
The angel said, 'Many of you can't handle it.

01:21:56.567 --> 01:22:08.640
' So I am only allowed to say what I'm allowed to say because it's all in my opinion.

01:22:08.640 --> 01:22:15.580
I'm not a financial adviser, but he that has ears to hear will hear it.

01:22:23.884 --> 01:22:29.295
You can't get mad at people's gain of what they've done when they buy XRP at 11 cents or other currencies at 5 cents and they went up to well over $3.

01:22:33.440 --> 01:22:35.856
And the Lord says, 'Sell when they go up, then I want you to buy it again.

01:22:35.856 --> 01:22:40.471
' Do you know how many times I've done that?

01:22:40.471 --> 01:22:43.280
You don't because it's none of your business.

01:22:43.280 --> 01:22:45.391
But I've done it, and the Lord has blessed me.

01:22:55.871 --> 01:22:56.200
People get mad about that.

01:22:56.200 --> 01:23:11.062
If you hear God, he'll tell you yourself, but you have wax in your ears so bad spiritually that he can't trust you with it because it will destroy you.

01:23:12.173 --> 01:23:12.840
And some of you are occultic.

01:23:12.840 --> 01:23:15.116
You're straight up from the devil.

01:23:15.116 --> 01:23:22.728
He'll never tell you the secret things because your heart's full of poison.

01:23:25.746 --> 01:23:38.878
But I'm going to tell you, God will show you the secret things too, and it will confound the wise.

01:23:52.676 --> 01:23:52.911
He wants it to be that you're the next Warren Buffett, the next Elon Musk.

01:23:52.911 --> 01:24:23.160
When I told you Satan came to me and he filled my house with this false light—it was gray—and he spoke to me.

01:24:23.160 --> 01:24:42.662
Satan spoke to me and he said, 'If you serve me with that gift, if you serve me with how you see, I'll make you worth billions.

01:24:42.662 --> 01:25:03.587
' He said, 'All you have to do is bow your knee to me and give your soul over to me, and I will make you very rich.

01:25:03.587 --> 01:25:07.387
' I'll never forget it.

01:25:07.387 --> 01:25:10.996
He had the most flowing, beautiful hair I've ever seen.

01:25:10.996 --> 01:25:16.430
He was beautiful, but his eyes were as black as onyx.

01:25:16.430 --> 01:25:26.720
He made me scared the moment he filled my house with this.

01:25:26.720 --> 01:25:28.408
He came as an angel of light.

01:25:28.408 --> 01:25:29.640
He said, 'You worship me.

01:25:29.640 --> 01:25:30.525
' I said, 'No.

01:25:30.525 --> 01:25:36.524
' And the more I kept praying in the Holy Spirit, he just sat there and laughed at me.

01:25:36.524 --> 01:25:41.034
Do you remember Thriller with Michael Jackson at the end?

